title: Pearl Jam - Unplugged
description:
As part of the recent release of the "legacy" edition of their Legendary album "TEN", Pearl Jam also included an Official DVD of their MTV UNPLUGGED preformance.

This is indeed a collector's item, as up to now, you could only get this on crappy, 2nd hand VHS copies.
